<template>
  <v-card v-for="item in estimates" :key="item.estimate_id">
  <v-card-title>{{ item.u_nsam }}</v-card-title>
  </v-card>vxcvghfg
</template>
<script setup>
import { useRoute } from "vue-router";
import { useStore } from "vuex";
import { ref, computed, onMounted } from "vue";
const route = useRoute();
const store = useStore();
const job_id = ref(route.params.job_id);
const estimates = computed(() => {
  return store.state.property.estimates;
});
onMounted(async () => {
  await store.dispatch("triggerSetEstimates", { job_id: job_id.value });
  console.log(estimates.value);
});
</script>
<style scoped></style>
